sequenceDiagram
    participant CRM System
    participant External Calendar
    participant User

    CRM System->>CRM System: Create Event (e.g., Invoice Due)
    CRM System->>External Calendar: Push new event details
    Note over External Calendar: (Google Calendar / Outlook)
    External Calendar->>User: Display event in calendar view
    User->>External Calendar: Update event (e.g., reschedule, add notes)
    External Calendar->>External Calendar: Save updated event
    External Calendar->>CRM System: Push updated event details
    CRM System->>CRM System: Update event in CRM database